{"tid":393784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台媒指疑似港男拒付2.6元膠袋費　與著名餅店店員罵戰","createTime":"2017-09-09T13:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T13:23:21.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47091267b72f649acd4cbac0d5da4c9497410a97","tid":393784,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">台媒指疑似港男拒付2.6元膠袋費　與著名餅店店員罵戰</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170909/s00004/fe823a7acf4f56b40a11f6ccbe98a380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170909%2Fs00004%2Ffe823a7acf4f56b40a11f6ccbe98a380.jpg&h=a0d2a1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣東森電視台報道，指一名疑似香港男遊客，在台北著名的佳德糕餅店，買了13盒糕餅，店員包裝後仍剩下3盒未能放入較小的膠袋。此時，這名男子要求店員給他一個較大膠袋裝下，但又不滿意店員加收膠袋徵費10元新台幣（約港幣2元6角），跟店員爭執長達5分鐘。其間男子指，自己買了那麼多糕餅，為何還要他給膠袋費，又曾將其他已放入膠袋的其他糕餅，大力擲下收銀台上洩憤。<br />\n<br />\n片段展示，店內其後開始有其他顧客覺得男子無理，其中3人上前要他不要為難店員。男子與同行另一男友人，反手指指對方及口角。<br />\n<br />\n有女店員事後接受東森電視台訪問稱，男顧客當時說要轉機到香港，要換一個更大的膠袋方便攜帶，且已買了幾千元新台幣糕餅，就不應該收他膠袋費。但店舖早已貼出告示，指為響應環保，顧客若要用大膠袋，便要收10元膠袋費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uvlJcfVCFVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuvlJcfVCFVM&d=hZWn5W61%2BZ1H4Qfd83okmQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=95c9228e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uvlJcfVCFVM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170909/s00004/1504944996045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170909%2Fs00004%2F1504944996045&d=hZWn5W61%2BZ1H4Qfd83okmQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2db58e89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170909%2Fs00004%2F1504944996045&h=8655ff14\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170909/s00004/1504944996045</a><br />\n<br />\n影衰香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28fc9ed547bf7be8123c76e7e4cbb2ac2a8a9fa","tid":393784,"uid":141804,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"763ce1dea7ded08e3a49e801b036d1864a681507","tid":393784,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"正常香港廢中廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed64d4b26294dcf2b5368f14a85f994dda7acb3","tid":393784,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常香港廢中廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係香港人黎，佢去香港轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad00abfb854d71b01545b6f572608639a5b9034","tid":393784,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"去香港轉機又點會係香港人，香港人係落機"},{"pid":"f61fe0c3f62ea585d3d180624e97f9f33b98e716","tid":393784,"uid":67028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"轉機去香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台北飛香港仲有得轉?"},{"pid":"11936a7f62b303168f6cfcda9ea46512f58757a0","tid":393784,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 市民自備環保袋緊係無問題啦<br />\n<br />\n但旅客點同？"}]}